Write a Java Program to calculate factorial value of a declared variable by creating separate class
and method for factorial segment.
class FactorialCalculator {
public int factorial(int num) {
int factorial = 1;
for (int i = 1; i <= num; i++) {
factorial *= i;
}
return factorial;
}
}
public class FactorialClass {
public static void main(String[] args) {
int num = 5;
FactorialCalculator calc = new FactorialCalculator();
int result = calc.factorial(num);
System.out.println("Factorial of " + num + " is: " + result);
}
}
